Installation 

  git clone git://github.com/snyd0r/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create Symlinks
      
  ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Install Vundle to ~/.vim/bundle

  git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle 

Install your plugins with 
 
 vim +BundleInstall +qall

Create Symlinks
      
  ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
